166
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:48,078
♪Cries fade in the smoke♪

167
00:13:48,902 --> 00:13:52,378
♪Storms gather♪

168
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:56,098
♪Glory falls like ashes♪

169
00:13:56,678 --> 00:13:59,898
♪Sleeves flutter♪

170
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:03,734
♪You sing of love and hate
on high stage♪

171
00:14:04,422 --> 00:14:07,819
♪Yearning brings only sorrow♪

172
00:14:08,070 --> 00:14:12,014
♪But in your eyes, I found resolve♪

173
00:14:14,022 --> 00:14:17,897
♪After one final song of parting♪

174
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:21,617
♪We'll meet again only through tears♪

175
00:14:21,617 --> 00:14:25,392
♪Silently, pain blossoms♪

176
00:14:25,542 --> 00:14:29,250
♪In the flames, we embrace♪

177
00:14:29,606 --> 00:14:33,168
♪After one last song of joy and grief♪

178
00:14:33,254 --> 00:14:36,960
♪Lovers sigh under the endless moon♪

179
